  "detailed_description": "AI Invasion is an action-loaded strategic top-down shooter in a futuristic setting. The superior machines subjugated the universe. In a wide range of missions you takes the role of a soldier to defend bases, escort convoys through enemy territory and reclaim occupied outposts. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nBut you don't fight alone. You have to equip and command a team of special units to achieve your ultimate goal:  The reclamation of the planet system.",
  "about_the_game": "AI Invasion is an action-loaded strategic top-down shooter in a futuristic setting. The superior machines subjugated the universe. In a wide range of missions you takes the role of a soldier to defend bases, escort convoys through enemy territory and reclaim occupied outposts. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nBut you don't fight alone. You have to equip and command a team of special units to achieve your ultimate goal:  The reclamation of the planet system.",
